text: Autostrada is the name used for a controlled-access highway in several languages. In English, it typically refers to the Autostrade of Italy. Autostrada may also refer to: ==By country== *Roads and expressways in Romania *Roads and expressways in Poland *Part of the network of transport in Albania *Autoestrada, express roads in Portugal ==See also== * Autoroute (disambiguation), the name used in French * Autobahn (disambiguation), the name used in German * Autopista (disambiguation), the name used in Spanish * Atlantia (company), Italian company formerly called Autostrade * Autostrad (band), Jordanian indie band
title: Autostrada (disambiguation)
